          p.caption (left) Checkboxes  |  (right) Screen: start a run
          img.project_img(src='img/strava/consistent_3.png', alt='2 screens showing consistency')
          p.caption_last (left) Screen: save activity  |  (right) Statistics bar and bottom nav
